1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:24,600
We've trained for years in this laying sword array. Our sword energy is flawless. Yet we couldn't even scratch him.

2
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:31,600
This demon lord is invincible. If we don't kill him today, the world will be doomed.

3
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:41,600
See that man in the block below? He's pretty weak, but good for practice. Go beat him, and today's lesson is done.

4
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:45,600
He's weak? But those three couldn't even touch him.

5
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:49,600
Eh, well they're even weaker. Go on. Go.

6
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:51,600
Just go.

7
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:28,599
Hmm.

8
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:32,599
Shouldn't even take two hits. Pretty weak.

9
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:36,599
Thank you, Master. May I know your name?

10
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:41,599
Master? I just beat a weakling.

11
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:43,799
Thank you, Master. May I know your name?

12
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:47,439
Master? I just beat a weakling.

13
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:57,599
He just called the demon lord.

14
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,799
Week?

15
00:02:07,919 --> 00:02:09,680
Find out who that Master is.

16
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:14,000
Anyone with information will be rewarded by the Celestial Academy.

17
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:16,080
You go search for him too.

18
00:02:16,319 --> 00:02:22,000
If he joins Soompay's set, all our secret manuals are here to take.

19
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:23,599
Thornbrose said go.

20
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:28,560
If this Master is willing to join us, all of the evil decided are his to choose the hardest.

21
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,640
Myself included.

22
00:02:31,119 --> 00:02:32,159
Uh.

23
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:41,279
Yannick, I was surprised it took you two moves to beat that guy in black.

24
00:02:41,919 --> 00:02:43,679
It's a bit long. You can do better.

25
00:02:43,679 --> 00:02:44,559
Oh, pathetic.

26
00:02:45,119 --> 00:02:46,879
Yes. I'll take your advice.

27
00:02:49,119 --> 00:02:52,879
Masters, I've trained here for eight years. Back then before I came here,

28
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:55,519
I dreamed of joining a sect called Celestial Academy.

29
00:02:55,519 --> 00:02:57,839
Now, the Desenial Disciple Trial's are starting soon.

30
00:02:58,479 --> 00:03:00,879
Though I'm still weak, I'd like to give it a shot.

31
00:03:01,599 --> 00:03:03,599
Is that so? You want to join them?

32
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:07,439
Hey, come on, having a vision is good thing.

33
00:03:07,439 --> 00:03:10,080
He's still young. We can't have him with us forever.

34
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:14,000
Yannick, go for it.

35
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:18,719
But remember, no matter where you go, we three will always have your back.

36
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:22,400
Thank you, Masters.

37
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,480
You, Brett. Here, take this.

38
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,759
Hey, you idiot.

39
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:31,759
This is Laura Fortune Nautis's treasure.

40
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:33,759
You better keep it safe.

41
00:03:33,759 --> 00:03:35,759
All right, Yannick, go on.

42
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:36,960
Go on.

43
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:37,759
Go on.

44
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:39,759
Go on, go on, go on, go on.

45
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:46,240
That token commands infinite wealth and he scoffs at it.

46
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:50,240
Once Yannick's left, things are about to get wild.
